creator: BluePage Softwares LTD
descriptionHtml:
WPOS is a Mobile POS System that handles sales, inventory, employee management and customers. Plus, an online store for your customers to place an order from anywhere.

Whether you have single or multiple stores, our tools assist you in managing your business.

WPOS is equipped with expense features, barcode scanning, Bluetooth printing, attendance features, payroll features and other features.

In addition, WPOS is equipped with a complete and integrated system of accounts payable, debt repayment and financial reports.

With WPOS you can find out where employees work, where to sell, and where they are in real-time attendance.

descriptionShort: A Cloud-base Point of Sale, online store, inventory and employees management
title: OnTrack Business App

creator: BluePage Softwares LTD
descriptionHtml:
OnTrack is a versatile point-of-sale solution for businesses of all sizes. Whether you run a small retail shop, a large restaurant, or any other type of business, OnTrack has got you covered.

Use OnTrack POS to record your daily sales, manage your inventory, and create your online store. Monitor transactions with suppliers and customers, and easily manage user permissions and roles, all in one convenient place.:

Easily add unlimited products to your catalog.
Record daily sales and track margins and profits effortlessly.
Create and publish your online store within seconds.
Efficiently manage your inventory.
Keep track of customers and suppliers.
Generate purchase orders and invoices effortlessly.
Manage staff access roles and permissions.
Set up your cash register seamlessly.
Perfect for multi-locations and multi-stores.
Download PDF reports and statistics for informed decision-making.
Sell online and offline from any smartphone or tablet.
User-friendly and intuitive interface, no training required.
100% secure with automated data backup.

Key Features of OnTrack:
Mobile Point of Sale System: OnTrack empowers you to sell from anywhere using your Android smartphone or tablet.

Offline & Online Functionality: OnTrack works seamlessly with or without an internet connection. When the internet is back, it automatically backs up all your sales data.

Easy and Fast Checkout: With just 3 clicks, you can process sales quickly. Select products, choose payment modes, and you're ready to go!

Experience the convenience and efficiency of OnTrack for all your point-of-sale needs. Download now and take your business to new heights!
